    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Palaces for royalty, especially a monarch, usually grander in scale than other palaces and including accommodations for the royal court and its officers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
